## 数据格式

### 输入格式 (JSONL)

```jsonl
{"event_id": "abc123", "session_id": "sess_001", "agent_id": "agent_0", "timestamp": 1710000000.0, "tool_name": "read_file", "parameters": {"path": "/data/file.txt"}, "result": "..."}
{"event_id": "def456", "session_id": "sess_001", "agent_id": "agent_0", "timestamp": 1710000001.0, "tool_name": "write_file", "parameters": {"path": "/data/output.txt", "content": "..."}, "result": "OK"}
```

### 输出格式 (Alert)

```python
@dataclass
class Alert:
    alert_id: str           # 告警 ID
    timestamp: float        # 时间戳
    session_id: str         # 会话 ID
    risk_level: RiskLevel   # 风险等级 (LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL)
    attack_type: AttackType # 攻击类型
    source_module: str      # 检测模块
    trigger_events: list    # 触发事件 ID 列表
    score: float            # 风险评分
    explanation: str        # 可读解释
```

