## 开发指南

### 添加新的检测模块

```python
# detection/my_detector.py
from callisto.collector.models import Alert, RiskLevel, AttackType

class MyDetector:
    def __init__(self, threshold: float = 0.5):
        self.threshold = threshold
    
    def detect(self, session: Session) -> Alert | None:
        # 实现检测逻辑
        score = self.compute_score(session)
        if score > self.threshold:
            return Alert(
                timestamp=time.time(),
                risk_level=RiskLevel.HIGH,
                attack_type=AttackType.A2_PRIV_ESCALATION,
                source_module="MyDetector",
                score=score,
                explanation="Custom detection logic triggered",
            )
        return None
```

### 运行测试

```bash
# 运行所有测试
pytest

# 运行特定模块测试
pytest tests/test_engine.py -v

# 生成覆盖率报告
pytest --cov=callisto --cov-report=html
```

